This documentary follows champion bodybuilder Ronnie Coleman as he trains for the annual Mr. Olympia contest. In addition to seeing him lifting in preparation, the filmmakers interview his nutritionist Chad Nichols. ~ Perry Seibert, All Movie Guide 2008
